          "headersSize": 573,
          "httpVersion": "HTTP/1.1",
          "method": "POST",
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n      <background>\\n        The user and agent have been brainstorming about their business idea.\\n      </background>\\n\\n      <topic>\\n        idea\\n      </topic>\\n\\n      <task>\\n        Read the recent chat history, and summarize their answer to: idea,\\n        preserving as much information as possible. This will be used to generate \\n        persuasive marketing copy, so be sure to capture all the details.\\n      </task>\\n      \\n      <chat-history>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"Tell us about your business. More info → better outcomes.\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"Friend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service.\\\\n            We help both sides: hosts get great content, guests get exposure,\\\\n            and we're the only platform that does this at scale.\\\\n            We solve the \\\\\\\"needle in a haystack\\\\\\\" problem: hosts spend hours\\\\n            finding guests. We do it in minutes with AI-powered filtering.\\\"</message>\\n</chat-history>\\n    \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1469,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1469,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01YSEbdTKr6NoKvNRK6H84q8\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Business Idea Summary: Friend of the Pod\\n\\n**Core Concept:**\\nFriend of the Pod is a podcast matchmaking service that connects podcast hosts with ideal guests through an AI-powered platform.\\n\\n**Problem Solved:**\\nAddresses the \\\"needle in a haystack\\\" problem where hosts spend hours manually searching for suitable guests. The platform reduces this to minutes through intelligent filtering.\\n\\n**Value Proposition - Dual-Sided Benefits:**\\n- **For Hosts:** Access to great content and guests quickly and efficiently\\n- **For Guests:** Gain exposure and media opportunities\\n- **For the Platform:** Operates at scale as the only service offering this comprehensive two-sided solution\\n\\n**Key Differentiator:**\\nAI-powered filtering technology that automates and accelerates the guest-host matching process, enabling rapid connections that would otherwise require extensive manual research.\\n\\n**Market Position:**\\nPositioned as the only platform operating at scale in this specific matchmaking niche, suggesting a first-mover or dominant market advantage.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":236,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":218,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
