          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1065,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01DvaHPKwwxMWeHZYPnYFsf9\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Solution Summary\\n\\n**Core Offering:** A 12-week progressive strength training program specifically designed for men in their 50s\\n\\n**Key Components:**\\n- **Frequency & Duration:** 3 sessions per week, 30 minutes each\\n- **Focus Areas:** Back and core strengthening\\n- **Delivery Method:** Video coaching\\n- **Target Benefit:** Accommodates busy schedules\\n\\n**Target Audience:** Busy men in their 50s\\n\\nThis solution addresses the specific needs of this demographic by combining time-efficient workouts with targeted strength training in areas critical for this age group, delivered through an accessible video format that fits into demanding schedules.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":202,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":144,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
